VSangita Kalanidhis: Gaambhirya Sangita Pravaham &#8211; Vols &#8211; 1 &amp; 2Sa Re Ga Ma, CD, Price: Rs. 175The two-volume album boasts samples by 14 of the Carnatic greats. Vol-1 has veterans including Ariyakudi, Chembai, Semmangudi, GNB, Madurai Mani Iyer, Maharajapuram Vishwanatha Iyer, Alathur Brothers and Balamuralikrishna singing one kriti. Vol &#8211; 2 has awardees such as K. V. Narayanaswamy, B. Rajam Iyer, Maharajapuram Santhanam, D. K. Jayaraman, T. V. Sankaranarayanan and T. N. Seshagopalan.One wonders on what basis the singers have been chosen, as many other great names such as &#8216;Flute&#8217; Mali, D.K. Pattammal and M.S. Subbulakshmi, to name a few, are missing.The two volumes just whet your musical appetite and are ideal for those who are just beginning to enjoy Carnatic music.
